{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The structural patch is in: the Compose file now lives under `infra/compose/`, there\u2019s a repo-level wrapper script in `scripts/`, and the new folder placeholders are in place for `migrations/`, `worker/`, `persistence/`, and test fixture...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_21", "text": "The structural patch is in: the Compose file now lives under `infra/compose/`, there\u2019s a repo-level wrapper script in `scripts/`, and the new folder placeholders are in place for `migrations/`, `worker/`, `persistence/`, and test fixtures. I\u2019m fixing script permissions and then validating the resulting layout and docs before I bring the stack up.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 42, "prompt_index": 2, "prompt_name": "01 \u2014 Monorepo Skeleton and Folder Layout", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T21:03:44-07:00"}
