{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the prompt-01 monorepo skeleton and checkpointed it in commit `b310953` (`feat(prompt-01): monorepo skeleton`). The main repo changes are the new infra home with the relocated Compose file at [infra/compose/docker-compose.yml...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_61", "text": "Implemented the prompt-01 monorepo skeleton and checkpointed it in commit `b310953` (`feat(prompt-01): monorepo skeleton`). The main repo changes are the new infra home with the relocated Compose file at [infra/compose/docker-compose.yml](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/infra/compose/docker-compose.yml), the developer wrapper at [scripts/dev-compose.sh](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/scripts/dev-compose.sh), the new placeholder directories and READMEs under `backend/`, `frontend/`, `docs/`, `infra/`, `scripts/`, `test-assets/`, and `tools/`, plus the updated tree snapshot and usage notes in [README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/README.md) and the matching structure update in [docs/architecture-overview.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/docs/architecture-overview.md).\n\nVerification passed through the supported Docker path: `./scripts/dev-compose.sh config`, `python -m compileall backend/app`, `./scripts/dev-compose.sh up -d --build`, health checks via `ps`, `curl` against backend and frontend, the browser smoke spec with screenshot output to `.artifacts/webapp-qa/homepage.png`, and a containerized `npm run build` for the frontend. The only failed check was the host-side `frontend` build because `vite` was not available in the local machine environment; the containerized build passed. The required reviewer summary was written last at [prompts/01-monorepo-skeleton.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/01-monorepo-skeleton.summary.md). Unrelated Yolopilot prompt artifact files remain outside the checkpoint commit by design.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 112, "prompt_index": 2, "prompt_name": "01 \u2014 Monorepo Skeleton and Folder Layout", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T21:07:11-07:00"}
